"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-shot-put-scientist-ryan-crouser-chases-historic-three-peat-in-paris\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"BORING, Ore. \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 Ryan Crouser is the greatest shot-putter who ever lived, a man who conquered his sport and has carried it upward, higher, and farther for nearly a decade.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 171, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17, \"end\": 29, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Crouser\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ryan Crouser\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Crouser\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Crouser\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Consider him a shot-put scientist, relying more on brain than brawn, but with plenty of both as he attempts this week to become the first shot-putter to win three straight gold medals.\", \"from\": 172, \"to\": 356, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But today\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Ryan Crouser is not quite the invincible Ryan Crouser of Rio and Tokyo, not for the last five months or so and not likely when he competes on Friday at Stade de France.\", \"from\": 358, \"to\": 540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 372, \"end\": 384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Crouser\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ryan Crouser\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Crouser\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Crouser\"}, {\"begin\": 437, \"end\": 442, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999668026818003, \"rank\": 1.7775339200814137e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 524, \"end\": 539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Crouser tore a pectoral muscle on April 11 during a routine bench press workout.\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 622, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt was bad,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d says Mitch, Ryan\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s father and lifelong coach.\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 688, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 646, \"end\": 651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"score\": 0.9999946121993922, \"rank\": 3.3144687221943572e-06, \"text\": \"Mitch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cCould be the end for a shot-putter.\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 727, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your pec is directly connected to the movement.\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 775, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just devastating.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  The muscle tear was on top of an injury to the ulnar nerve in his throwing elbow he suffered at the world indoor championships in Glasgow on March 1.\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 947, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 928, \"end\": 935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"score\": 0.8791148402900881, \"rank\": 0.13743626140857046, \"text\": \"Glasgow\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Ryan\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s elbow began hurting long before then.\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 998, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, his nerve had swelled tofive timesits normal size, causing severe pain.\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1079, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was cubital tunnel syndrome, which feels like hitting your funny bone over and over.\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1167, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ryan called the combination of the muscle tear and the elbow injury \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cuncomfortable.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d A mere mortal might call it \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cdebilitating.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Ryan had been addressing the sore elbow with treatment and physical therapy.\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1382, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1168, \"end\": 1172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.8747835550643055, \"rank\": 0.1424030819429196, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}, {\"begin\": 1306, \"end\": 1310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.8747835550637088, \"rank\": 0.1424030819429196, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But after tearing the pec, he abandoned the tweak-and-adapt approach.\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1452, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He had an ultrasound procedure, a nerve hydrodissection, to propel the nerve out of its groove with a saline solution.\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1571, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The nerve could then be freed from everything else (muscles, tissue, etc.).\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1647, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even after tearing the pec, Ryan still trained as much as he could.\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1716, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1677, \"end\": 1681, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.8747835550637088, \"rank\": 0.1424030819429196, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He just couldn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t throw\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094formonths.\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1754, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As trials drew near, in late June, neither Ryan nor Mitch had any real idea if Ryan could even qualify for Paris.\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1868, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1798, \"end\": 1802, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.8747835550637088, \"rank\": 0.1424030819429196, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}, {\"begin\": 1807, \"end\": 1812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"score\": 0.9999999469117725, \"rank\": 4.9506213844482536e-08, \"text\": \"Mitch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\"}, {\"begin\": 1834, \"end\": 1838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.8747835550637088, \"rank\": 0.1424030819429196, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}, {\"begin\": 1862, \"end\": 1867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9988458239523611, \"rank\": 0.00115550970778547, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At least the trials would be at Hayward Field, where two of Ryan\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s uncles had starred.\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1957, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was Ryan\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s home field, site of his first Junior Olympics, first national championship and other indelible moments.\", \"from\": 1958, \"to\": 2077, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But had the injury healed enough to even compete?\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2127, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Had it healed enough to make the national team?\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2175, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Enough to train an additional six weeks afterward to prepare for Paris?\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2247, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2241, \"end\": 2246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999432097576819, \"rank\": 5.679346748888838e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The afternoon after he injured his pec, Ryan called his father.\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2312, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2289, \"end\": 2293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9981267081859916, \"rank\": 0.0017889617618315704, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He explained the injury, the pain, the doubts.\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2359, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As Ryan hung up, Mitch heard him say he wanted to be alone.\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2419, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2363, \"end\": 2367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9981267081859916, \"rank\": 0.0017889617618315704, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}, {\"begin\": 2377, \"end\": 2382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"score\": 0.9999825266629405, \"rank\": 1.7395965820502854e-05, \"text\": \"Mitch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He needed to process this.\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2446, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One morning, he was preparing to seize another gold.\", \"from\": 2447, \"to\": 2499, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That night, he was wondering if his career was finished.\", \"from\": 2500, \"to\": 2556, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But process it he did.\", \"from\": 2558, \"to\": 2580, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The next day, unable to find Ryan, one of his training partners went to the place he knew he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d be\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094the \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cshop\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d where they lift weights.\", \"from\": 2581, \"to\": 2722, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2610, \"end\": 2614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9981267081859916, \"rank\": 0.0017889617618315704, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There he was:pumping iron.\", \"from\": 2723, \"to\": 2749, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He had figured out a way to do that without risking further damage to the elbow or the pec muscle.\", \"from\": 2750, \"to\": 2848, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ryan Crouser figures stuff out.\", \"from\": 2850, \"to\": 2881, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2850, \"end\": 2862, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Crouser\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ryan Crouser\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Crouser\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Crouser\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the University of Texas, he loved economics and engineering classes, and he obtained a Master\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s in finance.\", \"from\": 2882, \"to\": 2994, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He generally approaches life like a personal science experiment.\", \"from\": 2995, \"to\": 3059, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After winning his first gold medal, in Rio, Ryan wanted to throw farther, as far as humanly possible.\", \"from\": 3061, \"to\": 3162, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3100, \"end\": 3103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 0.9852661818577871, \"rank\": 0.014948685963652286, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}, {\"begin\": 3105, \"end\": 3109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9993925401648164, \"rank\": 0.000594075348838333, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, he sought microscopic advances: in nutrition, sleep and training techniques.\", \"from\": 3163, \"to\": 3243, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Such analytical drive runs in the family.\", \"from\": 3244, \"to\": 3285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To call the Crousers a family of throwers doesn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t quite capture the depth of their collective involvement in the throwing disciplines.\", \"from\": 3287, \"to\": 3423, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Long before Ryan was around,Sports Illustrateddispatched its legendary track writer, Kenny Moore, to Boring, Ore., to profile Mitch, his brother Dean and their younger brother, Brian, in 1983.\", \"from\": 3424, \"to\": 3616, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3436, \"end\": 3440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9993925401648164, \"rank\": 0.000594075348838333, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}, {\"begin\": 3509, \"end\": 3520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Moore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.767409323260426e-15, \"text\": \"Kenny Moore\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Moore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Moore\"}, {\"begin\": 3525, \"end\": 3531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boredom\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.086401780572727e-15, \"text\": \"Boring\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boredom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boredom\"}, {\"begin\": 3550, \"end\": 3555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"score\": 0.9999991246007051, \"rank\": 8.375071486811137e-07, \"text\": \"Mitch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\"}, {\"begin\": 3569, \"end\": 3573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"score\": 0.9998254023834191, \"rank\": 9.335768103631806e-05, \"text\": \"Dean\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The story was teased on the cover: \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cBrother, Are They Armed!\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Ryan\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s grandfather, Larry, was the family patriarch.\", \"from\": 3617, \"to\": 3738, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He never pushed any of his children into throwing, but one day he brought home a barbell and issued a challenge: \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIf you can clean-and-jerk 40 pounds, I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll buy you a shot.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  The boys met the challenge and Larry made good on his promise.\", \"from\": 3739, \"to\": 3981, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They took turns throwing the shot all over a vacant lot next door.\", \"from\": 3982, \"to\": 4048, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If they made 50 proper throws, Larry would get them a discus.\", \"from\": 4049, \"to\": 4110, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If they did the same with the discus, he would get them what Dean calls the Holy Grail of throwing objects\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094ajavelin.\", \"from\": 4111, \"to\": 4229, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4172, \"end\": 4176, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deathlands\", \"score\": 0.9026952487913933, \"rank\": 0.10711974321029533, \"text\": \"Dean\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deathlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deathlands\"}, {\"begin\": 4187, \"end\": 4197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Holy_Grail\", \"score\": 0.9261334284512395, \"rank\": 0.07975802324520062, \"text\": \"Holy Grail\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Holy_Grail\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Holy_Grail\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mitch, now 67, would become an alternate on the 1984 Olympic discus team.\", \"from\": 4231, \"to\": 4304, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4231, \"end\": 4236, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"score\": 0.9999998069289591, \"rank\": 1.765569698154824e-07, \"text\": \"Mitch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dean, 64,\\u00c2\\u00a0 still holds the University of Oregon records in the discus and shot.\", \"from\": 4305, \"to\": 4385, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4305, \"end\": 4309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deathlands\", \"score\": 0.9026952487913933, \"rank\": 0.10711974321029533, \"text\": \"Dean\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deathlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deathlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brian, 61, competed in two Olympics in the javelin.\", \"from\": 4386, \"to\": 4437, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Eventually, the brothers started a business training athletes; initially, as wholesale distributors, selling nutrition plans, athletic equipment and training regimens.\", \"from\": 4439, \"to\": 4606, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They had a barn and they put up a large, industrial-strength, commercial-grade net, purchased at a nearby Army surplus store, the kind used to lower soldiers from helicopters (i.e.,Crouserstrong), for their pupils to throw into.\", \"from\": 4607, \"to\": 4835, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4713, \"end\": 4731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Surplus_store\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Army surplus store\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Surplus_store\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Surplus_store\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They drew a circle on the concrete floor and started running drills.\", \"from\": 4836, \"to\": 4904, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And they trained their sons too.\", \"from\": 4906, \"to\": 4938, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even in the First Family of Throwers, Ryan stood out early on.\", \"from\": 4940, \"to\": 5002, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4978, \"end\": 4982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9987716191232153, \"rank\": 0.0012296660501920677, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He insisted on making 30 throws every day, and despite the net\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s strength, he and the rest of this family of throwers would wear through one in a year or two.\", \"from\": 5003, \"to\": 5163, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As a high school freshman, he scribbled goals on the walls of the barn.\", \"from\": 5164, \"to\": 5235, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One day, he asked his father, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWhat would it take to win state?\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  In Oregon, the answer is: more than in most other places.\", \"from\": 5236, \"to\": 5363, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5309, \"end\": 5315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\", \"score\": 0.6974454024565369, \"rank\": 0.2963547714720351, \"text\": \"Oregon\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Around 60 feet in the shot put, Mitch told him.\", \"from\": 5364, \"to\": 5411, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5396, \"end\": 5401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"score\": 0.9999982746094352, \"rank\": 1.4130304396713878e-06, \"text\": \"Mitch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cO.K.,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Ryan responded.\", \"from\": 5412, \"to\": 5439, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWhat would it take for me to do that?\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Training, Mitch said.\", \"from\": 5440, \"to\": 5506, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5495, \"end\": 5500, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"score\": 0.9999982746094352, \"rank\": 1.4130304396713878e-06, \"text\": \"Mitch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He laid out drills and routines for Ryan.\", \"from\": 5507, \"to\": 5548, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5543, \"end\": 5547, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.975086472477264, \"rank\": 0.025549873661519444, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every day, he made 30 throws, lifted weights, did precisely as Mitch instructed.\", \"from\": 5549, \"to\": 5629, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5612, \"end\": 5617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"score\": 0.9999982746094352, \"rank\": 1.4130304396713878e-06, \"text\": \"Mitch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The secret?\", \"from\": 5630, \"to\": 5641, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Popsicle sticks, of course.\", \"from\": 5642, \"to\": 5669, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the end of a practice, Mitch would mark out a spot farther than Ryan had thrown, and stick a popsicle stick in the ground.\", \"from\": 5670, \"to\": 5795, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5696, \"end\": 5701, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"score\": 0.9999982746094352, \"rank\": 1.4130304396713878e-06, \"text\": \"Mitch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\"}, {\"begin\": 5737, \"end\": 5741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.975086472477264, \"rank\": 0.025549873661519444, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ryan\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s attempts almost always flew past the stick.\", \"from\": 5796, \"to\": 5848, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As a freshman, Ryan put the shot around 40 feet.\", \"from\": 5850, \"to\": 5898, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5865, \"end\": 5869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.999672574885406, \"rank\": 0.0003264306914935473, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Soon, he got above 60.\", \"from\": 5899, \"to\": 5921, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One freezing night, Mitch went outside looking for Ryan.\", \"from\": 5922, \"to\": 5978, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5942, \"end\": 5947, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"score\": 0.9999801637924912, \"rank\": 1.2892533523807374e-05, \"text\": \"Mitch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\"}, {\"begin\": 5973, \"end\": 5977, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.999672574885406, \"rank\": 0.0003264306914935473, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He saw a window open, and spied his son.\", \"from\": 5979, \"to\": 6019, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Doing power cleans.\", \"from\": 6020, \"to\": 6039, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Steam rising off his shoulders.\", \"from\": 6040, \"to\": 6071, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cHow long do you think that will last?\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Lisa asked Mitch.\", \"from\": 6072, \"to\": 6133, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6116, \"end\": 6120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Simpson\", \"score\": 0.9999269288598539, \"rank\": 3.6261162487702374e-05, \"text\": \"Lisa\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Simpson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Simpson\"}, {\"begin\": 6127, \"end\": 6132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"score\": 0.9999801637924912, \"rank\": 1.2892533523807374e-05, \"text\": \"Mitch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He answered, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWe\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll see.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Ryan\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s final throw at state that year sailed 60\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00993\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d.\", \"from\": 6134, \"to\": 6224, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He won, becoming the first freshman state champion in a state with a proud track history.\", \"from\": 6225, \"to\": 6314, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was only 14.\", \"from\": 6315, \"to\": 6330, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He loved chocolate, and his grandfather promised him a four-pound Hershey\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s bar if he won state.\", \"from\": 6331, \"to\": 6429, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When he did, Ryan didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t wax on about his place in history.\", \"from\": 6430, \"to\": 6491, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He went right up to Larry and asked about the chocolate.\", \"from\": 6492, \"to\": 6548, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When it came time for college, Ryan chose Texas, not ballyhooed and nearby Oregon.\", \"from\": 6550, \"to\": 6632, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6581, \"end\": 6585, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.999672574885406, \"rank\": 0.0003264306914935473, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}, {\"begin\": 6592, \"end\": 6597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Longhorns\", \"score\": 0.8836677847396633, \"rank\": 0.07619311106857816, \"text\": \"Texas\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Longhorns\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Longhorns\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ryan found success in Austin, winning four national titles, two indoor and two outdoor, and becoming a nine-time All-America.\", \"from\": 6633, \"to\": 6758, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6633, \"end\": 6637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.999672574885406, \"rank\": 0.0003264306914935473, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}, {\"begin\": 6655, \"end\": 6661, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stone_Cold_Steve_Austin\", \"score\": 0.7173358704648292, \"rank\": 0.24351792525583918, \"text\": \"Austin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stone_Cold_Steve_Austin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stone_Cold_Steve_Austin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ryan was successful in the classroom too.\", \"from\": 6759, \"to\": 6800, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6759, \"end\": 6763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.8975904989305845, \"rank\": 0.11409179700261281, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The former Sam Barlow High valedictorian won All-Academic honors at UT.\", \"from\": 6801, \"to\": 6872, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6812, \"end\": 6822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Barlow_(pioneer)\", \"score\": 0.5937031484089639, \"rank\": 0.6464646464646785, \"text\": \"Sam Barlow\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Barlow_(pioneer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Barlow_(pioneer)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2013, Ryan tore a ligament in his throwing hand and came down with a savage throat infection.\", \"from\": 6874, \"to\": 6970, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6883, \"end\": 6887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.8975904989305845, \"rank\": 0.11409179700261281, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The combination forced him to redshirt.\", \"from\": 6971, \"to\": 7010, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He also teetered academically for the first time and decided to switch majors, from engineering to economics.\", \"from\": 7011, \"to\": 7120, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He rebounded and graduated on time with another year of athletic eligibility remaining.\", \"from\": 7122, \"to\": 7209, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Master\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s in finance?\", \"from\": 7210, \"to\": 7232, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Why not!\", \"from\": 7233, \"to\": 7241, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One problem.\", \"from\": 7242, \"to\": 7254, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His scholarship ended after one more year, but the Master\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s was a two-year program.\", \"from\": 7255, \"to\": 7340, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The cost of the second year would land around $60,000.\", \"from\": 7341, \"to\": 7395, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ryan\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s solution: Complete the degree in a single year,whileexhausting his eligibility in track and field.\", \"from\": 7396, \"to\": 7503, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ryan slept four hours a night.\", \"from\": 7505, \"to\": 7535, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7505, \"end\": 7509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.8975904989305845, \"rank\": 0.11409179700261281, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He practicedafterstudying, in the light cast by his truck\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s headlights.\", \"from\": 7536, \"to\": 7609, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He surpassed 70 feet in 2016, at Big 12 indoors, while tying the NCAA indoor mark of 21.73 meters (nearly 71.3 feet).\", \"from\": 7610, \"to\": 7727, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7675, \"end\": 7679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"score\": 0.9575398594016535, \"rank\": 0.04434289555056139, \"text\": \"NCAA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rio was now a real possibility, but the mental and physical toll was becoming too much.\", \"from\": 7728, \"to\": 7815, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He summoned the courage to call Mitch.\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m done.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  He explained.\", \"from\": 7816, \"to\": 7891, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"NFL scouts were calling.\", \"from\": 7892, \"to\": 7916, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7892, \"end\": 7895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2010_NFL_season\", \"score\": 0.8705021749347015, \"rank\": 0.14779818825517407, \"text\": \"NFL\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2010_NFL_season\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2010_NFL_season\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They wanted to develop him as a pass rusher, send him to the combine, then team tryouts, where he could vie for a practice squad spot.\", \"from\": 7917, \"to\": 8051, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The minimum salary was $400,000.\", \"from\": 8052, \"to\": 8084, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mitch flipped in an instant, from coach-dad tojust dad.\", \"from\": 8086, \"to\": 8141, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8086, \"end\": 8091, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"score\": 0.9999950780541605, \"rank\": 4.4944204258056795e-06, \"text\": \"Mitch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He noted, gently, that Ryan had much more shot put in him.\", \"from\": 8142, \"to\": 8200, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8165, \"end\": 8169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.8450888548412694, \"rank\": 0.18258398863543598, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If, that is, he wanted to come back.\", \"from\": 8201, \"to\": 8237, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIf you don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t have that drive anymore, I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll support you inanything,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Mitch said.\", \"from\": 8238, \"to\": 8326, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8315, \"end\": 8320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"score\": 0.9999950780541605, \"rank\": 4.4944204258056795e-06, \"text\": \"Mitch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWe\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll start training for the combine.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  That was that \\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 for a whole week!\", \"from\": 8327, \"to\": 8409, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When one of his Longhorn teammates asked Ryan for training help, he accepted.\", \"from\": 8410, \"to\": 8487, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8451, \"end\": 8455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.8450888548412694, \"rank\": 0.18258398863543598, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Training another human sparked the drive that still simmered in Ryan.\", \"from\": 8488, \"to\": 8557, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8552, \"end\": 8556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.8450888548412694, \"rank\": 0.18258398863543598, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He called Mitch at the end of the week.Hey,I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m gonna make my comeback!\", \"from\": 8558, \"to\": 8630, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8568, \"end\": 8573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"score\": 0.9999950780541605, \"rank\": 4.4944204258056795e-06, \"text\": \"Mitch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ryan won the 2016 trials, and the Crousers flew to Rio.\", \"from\": 8632, \"to\": 8687, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8632, \"end\": 8636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.8450888548412694, \"rank\": 0.18258398863543598, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}, {\"begin\": 8683, \"end\": 8686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 0.8293287130399594, \"rank\": 0.20578572778462084, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At first, Dean wondered if Ryan could even make the final.\", \"from\": 8688, \"to\": 8746, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8698, \"end\": 8702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"score\": 0.994973721739946, \"rank\": 0.003467540219386304, \"text\": \"Dean\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\"}, {\"begin\": 8715, \"end\": 8719, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9999999724012699, \"rank\": 2.358048164316456e-08, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then MItch and Dean watched him practice.\", \"from\": 8747, \"to\": 8788, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8762, \"end\": 8766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"score\": 0.994973721739946, \"rank\": 0.003467540219386304, \"text\": \"Dean\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After about a week, Dean said, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t want to jinx him, but I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m not so sure that Ryan can\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099tmedal.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Three days later, he said, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cActually, silver wouldn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t be too crazy.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Ryan made the final with ease.\", \"from\": 8789, \"to\": 9006, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8809, \"end\": 8813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"score\": 0.994973721739946, \"rank\": 0.003467540219386304, \"text\": \"Dean\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\"}, {\"begin\": 8878, \"end\": 8882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9999999724012699, \"rank\": 2.358048164316456e-08, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}, {\"begin\": 8976, \"end\": 8980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9999999724012699, \"rank\": 2.358048164316456e-08, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He then sailed one 22.52 meters.\", \"from\": 9007, \"to\": 9039, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He hadn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t just medaled.\", \"from\": 9040, \"to\": 9065, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He wongold, in his firstOlympics.\", \"from\": 9066, \"to\": 9099, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ryan broke the Olympic record, which had stood since Ulf Timmermann of East Germany set the mark in 1988.When reporters asked Ryan if he had ever imagined doing what he had just done, his answer: of course.\", \"from\": 9101, \"to\": 9307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9101, \"end\": 9105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9999999724012699, \"rank\": 2.358048164316456e-08, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}, {\"begin\": 9154, \"end\": 9168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulf_Timmermann\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ulf Timmermann\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulf_Timmermann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulf_Timmermann\"}, {\"begin\": 9172, \"end\": 9184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Germany\", \"score\": 0.7522194029120141, \"rank\": 0.3293987149071303, \"text\": \"East Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Germany\"}, {\"begin\": 9227, \"end\": 9231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9999999724012699, \"rank\": 2.358048164316456e-08, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He knew he had already broken that Olympic record maybe 10,000 times, aimingjustpast another popsicle stick.\", \"from\": 9308, \"to\": 9416, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There have been 352 throws past 22 meters.\", \"from\": 9418, \"to\": 9460, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Eight men have bested 22 at least once.\", \"from\": 9461, \"to\": 9500, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Four of the all-time leaders are still competing: Leonardo Fabbri of Italy has thrown 22 meters 13 times; Tom Walsh of New Zealand, 40; Joe Kovacs of the U.S., 41; and Ryan Crouser,86!\", \"from\": 9501, \"to\": 9685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9551, \"end\": 9566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_Fabbri\", \"score\": 0.999997710495001, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Leonardo Fabbri\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_Fabbri\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_Fabbri\"}, {\"begin\": 9570, \"end\": 9575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8879634766031886, 