858, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Of the 51 best shot puts in history, the two men account for44of them.\", \"from\": 9859, \"to\": 9929, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And, together, they own the 11 best marks in the sport.\", \"from\": 9930, \"to\": 9985, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Several years back, the analytical Ryan began to calibrate his throws, based on conditions and his health, with more and more accuracy.\", \"from\": 9987, \"to\": 10122, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10022, \"end\": 10026, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9999836803951146, \"rank\": 1.6197183775977727e-05, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dean would ask Mitch what they wanted to throw at a meet, and Ryan would throw, almost always,exactly that.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cHe\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s like a human tape measure,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Mitch says.\", \"from\": 10123, \"to\": 10281, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10123, \"end\": 10127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"score\": 0.9991948801642621, \"rank\": 0.0004409810725203725, \"text\": \"Dean\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\"}, {\"begin\": 10138, \"end\": 10143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"score\": 0.9999999857128615, \"rank\": 9.782639755238421e-09, \"text\": \"Mitch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\"}, {\"begin\": 10185, \"end\": 10189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9999836803951146, \"rank\": 1.6197183775977727e-05, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}, {\"begin\": 10270, \"end\": 10275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"score\": 0.9999999857128615, \"rank\": 9.782639755238421e-09, \"text\": \"Mitch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After Rio, Larry Crouser gave his grandson a message:Break the world record.\", \"from\": 10283, \"to\": 10359, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10289, \"end\": 10292, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 0.9957006548020914, \"rank\": 0.004317235980197584, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Larry was sick then, with Parkinson\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s.\", \"from\": 10360, \"to\": 10400, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ryan chased the mark like he chased everything: full-bore.\", \"from\": 10401, \"to\": 10459, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10401, \"end\": 10405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9999836803951146, \"rank\": 1.6197183775977727e-05, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He topped it first in practice, heaving a shot past\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094what else?\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094a popsicle stick.\", \"from\": 10460, \"to\": 10544, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cGod, when is he gonna break that record?\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Larry kept asking.\", \"from\": 10546, \"to\": 10611, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s not that easy, dad,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Mitch would respond.\", \"from\": 10613, \"to\": 10666, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10646, \"end\": 10651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"score\": 0.9996743202611007, \"rank\": 0.0003256665455158751, \"text\": \"Mitch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In May 2021, at the USATF Throws Fest in Arizona, Ryan put a shot 23.01\\u00c2\\u00a0meters, .05 meters short of the record.\", \"from\": 10668, \"to\": 10780, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10688, \"end\": 10693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Track_&_Field\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USATF\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Track_&_Field\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Track_&_Field\"}, {\"begin\": 10709, \"end\": 10716, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona\", \"score\": 0.958697807103564, \"rank\": 0.021309954582698177, \"text\": \"Arizona\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona\"}, {\"begin\": 10718, \"end\": 10722, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9995949083675004, \"rank\": 0.000260494346167512, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The next month, U.S. Olympic trials were in Eugene.\", \"from\": 10781, \"to\": 10832, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Larry\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s health was declining.\", \"from\": 10833, \"to\": 10864, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On June 18, Ryan catapulted a shot 23.37 meters (nearly 76.7 feet)\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094a world record.\", \"from\": 10865, \"to\": 10949, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10877, \"end\": 10881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9995949083675004, \"rank\": 0.000260494346167512, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The next day, Ryan stopped by his grandfather\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s place.\", \"from\": 10951, \"to\": 11007, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10965, \"end\": 10969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9995949083675004, \"rank\": 0.000260494346167512, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Larry couldn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t hear at all by then.\", \"from\": 11008, \"to\": 11045, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He communicated primarily via a small whiteboard.\", \"from\": 11046, \"to\": 11095, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ryan grabbed a sharpie and began to write.\", \"from\": 11096, \"to\": 11138, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11096, \"end\": 11100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9995949083675004, \"rank\": 0.000260494346167512, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then he turned the board around.\", \"from\": 11139, \"to\": 11171, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It read: \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI broke the world record.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d As Larry read it, the largest smile spread across his face.\", \"from\": 11172, \"to\": 11272, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Larry died a few weeks later, the day before Ryan left for Tokyo.\", \"from\": 11274, \"to\": 11339, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11319, \"end\": 11323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9995949083675004, \"rank\": 0.000260494346167512, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}, {\"begin\": 11333, \"end\": 11338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9859476737507333, \"rank\": 0.013650039668668512, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ryan didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t break the world record there, but he did win the gold medal.\", \"from\": 11340, \"to\": 11414, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11340, \"end\": 11344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9995949083675004, \"rank\": 0.000260494346167512, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Afterward, he held a sign up for the TV cameras that he had written beforehand:\\u00c2  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cGRANDPA, WE DID IT!\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Lisa keeps most of Ryan\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s trophies and awards in their attic.\", \"from\": 11415, \"to\": 11587, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11524, \"end\": 11528, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Simpson\", \"score\": 0.9999998493009457, \"rank\": 1.4645752113896071e-07, \"text\": \"Lisa\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Simpson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Simpson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ryan doesn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t have much use for them.\", \"from\": 11588, \"to\": 11626, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11588, \"end\": 11592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9999923202477011, \"rank\": 4.535692481996815e-06, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When his beloved grandfather started struggling to speak and hear, the two began writing letters back and forth.\", \"from\": 11627, \"to\": 11739, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Recently, Mitch noticed a box in Ryan\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s house in Arkansas.\", \"from\": 11740, \"to\": 11800, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11750, \"end\": 11755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"score\": 0.9999898021882677, \"rank\": 9.58251341864122e-06, \"text\": \"Mitch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He had savedevery single letter from Larry.\", \"from\": 11801, \"to\": 11844, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even with the loaded shot put field at the 2024 U.S. trials\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094six throwers were in the 22-plus club\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094a healthy Ryan Crowser would finish in the top three.\", \"from\": 11846, \"to\": 12001, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11958, \"end\": 11962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9999923202477011, \"rank\": 4.535692481996815e-06, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he was not healthy, of course.\\u00c2  Ryan had skipped meets.\", \"from\": 12002, \"to\": 12062, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12039, \"end\": 12043, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9999923202477011, \"rank\": 4.535692481996815e-06, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He hadn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t thrown for months.\", \"from\": 12063, \"to\": 12093, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When Dean rode with Mitch to Eugene, he pumped him for information.\", \"from\": 12094, \"to\": 12161, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12099, \"end\": 12103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"score\": 0.9999343823847507, \"rank\": 6.436368385665427e-05, \"text\": \"Dean\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\"}, {\"begin\": 12114, \"end\": 12119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"score\": 0.9999898021882677, \"rank\": 9.58251341864122e-06, \"text\": \"Mitch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cHow\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s it feeling?\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Dean asked.\", \"from\": 12162, \"to\": 12199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12188, \"end\": 12192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"score\": 0.9999343823847507, \"rank\": 6.436368385665427e-05, \"text\": \"Dean\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rather than answer directly, Mitch told his brother the marks Ryan hoped to hit, both in qualifying and the final round.\", \"from\": 12201, \"to\": 12321, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12230, \"end\": 12235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"score\": 0.9999898021882677, \"rank\": 9.58251341864122e-06, \"text\": \"Mitch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\"}, {\"begin\": 12263, \"end\": 12267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9999923202477011, \"rank\": 4.535692481996815e-06, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t expect Ryan to beat Kovacs at trials; he hoped Ryan, with six additional weeks to rest, recover and train, could beat Kovacs in Paris.\", \"from\": 12322, \"to\": 12468, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12341, \"end\": 12345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9999997953260827, \"rank\": 1.4314426907466733e-07, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}, {\"begin\": 12381, \"end\": 12385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9999997953260827, \"rank\": 1.4314426907466733e-07, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}, {\"begin\": 12462, \"end\": 12467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999287515362375, \"rank\": 7.125354024093553e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mitch kept to himself the worst case: What if Ryan can\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t throw?\", \"from\": 12469, \"to\": 12534, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12515, \"end\": 12519, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9999997953260827, \"rank\": 1.4314426907466733e-07, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But, just as in Rio, Ryan hit every mark his father had laid out, nearly to the inch.\", \"from\": 12536, \"to\": 12621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12552, \"end\": 12555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 0.9862553186870714, \"rank\": 0.01393602400531724, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}, {\"begin\": 12557, \"end\": 12561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9999997953260827, \"rank\": 1.4314426907466733e-07, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The first time he actually threw a shot in weeks wasat trials(!\", \"from\": 12622, \"to\": 12685, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"),in qualifying(!).\", \"from\": 12685, \"to\": 12704, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t exert top energy in the first round but still registered a 21.44-meter throw (70.3 feet), third-best overall.\", \"from\": 12705, \"to\": 12826, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A similar mark in the final wouldn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t be good enough to make the Olympic team.\", \"from\": 12828, \"to\": 12907, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(He would have finished seventh.)\", \"from\": 12908, \"to\": 12941, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As usual, Ryan was the last athlete to leave the stadium after the first night of qualifying.\", \"from\": 12942, \"to\": 13035, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12952, \"end\": 12956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9999997953260827, \"rank\": 1.4314426907466733e-07, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He signed autographs, took pictures, did interviews.\", \"from\": 13036, \"to\": 13088, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then drug testing.\", \"from\": 13089, \"to\": 13107, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then dinner, with roughly 30 friends and relatives.\", \"from\": 13108, \"to\": 13159, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What struck Dean was how calm his nephew seemed.\", \"from\": 13160, \"to\": 13208, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the final, Ryan heaved one attempt 22.84 glorious meters (roughly 74.9 feet).\", \"from\": 13210, \"to\": 13290, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13224, \"end\": 13228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9995421714347436, \"rank\": 0.00042288384971088237, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He beat Kovacs.\", \"from\": 13291, \"to\": 13306, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He won the trials.\", \"from\": 13307, \"to\": 13325, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He qualified for Paris.\", \"from\": 13326, \"to\": 13349, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13343, \"end\": 13348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999603736688639, \"rank\": 3.962790102325083e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cProbably his best performance,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Dean says, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cconsidering the circumstances.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Afterward, all Ryan kept saying was, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI got six more weeks.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s June and Mitch is talking about limits and bodies.\", \"from\": 13350, \"to\": 13559, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13387, \"end\": 13391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"score\": 0.9961958609653117, \"rank\": 0.0021652543903889496, \"text\": \"Dean\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\"}, {\"begin\": 13451, \"end\": 13455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9995421714347436, \"rank\": 0.00042288384971088237, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}, {\"begin\": 13518, \"end\": 13523, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"score\": 0.9999999986206376, \"rank\": 1.0473946762694936e-09, \"text\": \"Mitch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Limits, these supposedly unmoveable ceilings, have changed over time.\", \"from\": 13560, \"to\": 13629, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Many athletes, Mitch says, focus on qualifying and winning, but Ryan always asks:How far can I take this thing?\", \"from\": 13630, \"to\": 13741, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13645, \"end\": 13650, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"score\": 0.9999999986206376, \"rank\": 1.0473946762694936e-09, \"text\": \"Mitch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\"}, {\"begin\": 13694, \"end\": 13698, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9995421714347436, \"rank\": 0.00042288384971088237, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kovacs, Ryan\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s primary competition, can squat 700 pounds, clean-and-jerk more than 600.\", \"from\": 13743, \"to\": 13832, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dude isZeus-strong.\", \"from\": 13833, \"to\": 13852, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Joe is six-feet tall, seven inches shorter than Ryan.\", \"from\": 13853, \"to\": 13906, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13853, \"end\": 13856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"score\": 0.9749686898268839, \"rank\": 0.013938883997869633, \"text\": \"Joe\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\"}, {\"begin\": 13901, \"end\": 13905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9995421714347436, \"rank\": 0.00042288384971088237, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Ryan is actually a little tootallto throw as far or as hard as he possibly could.\", \"from\": 13907, \"to\": 13992, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13911, \"end\": 13915, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9995421714347436, \"rank\": 0.00042288384971088237, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Were the shot-put ring a bit larger, Ryan could implement a longer set-up.\", \"from\": 13993, \"to\": 14067, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14030, \"end\": 14034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9995421714347436, \"rank\": 0.00042288384971088237, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For someone to come along and surpass Ryan, Mitch ventures that he will have to be slightly shorter than Ryan \\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6and\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 as strong as Kovac.\", \"from\": 14069, \"to\": 14208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14107, \"end\": 14111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9995421714347436, \"rank\": 0.00042288384971088237, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}, {\"begin\": 14174, \"end\": 14178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9995421714347436, \"rank\": 0.00042288384971088237, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But that person may never come along.\", \"from\": 14209, \"to\": 14246, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ryan\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s world record, set in Los Angeles in May 2023, traveled 23.56 meters (nearly 77.3 feet).\", \"from\": 14248, \"to\": 14344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14278, \"end\": 14289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999785381507783, \"rank\": 6.31302905660389e-06, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Can he top that?\", \"from\": 14345, \"to\": 14361, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe.\", \"from\": 14362, \"to\": 14368, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But maybe he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s also, Mitch wonders, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cat the upper limit of what a taller guy can do.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\\u00c2  Ryan would compete in the shot forever if he could, but that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s not possible.\", \"from\": 14369, \"to\": 14541, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14392, \"end\": 14397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"score\": 0.9999999173094273, \"rank\": 7.389585343232066e-08, \"text\": \"Mitch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\"}, {\"begin\": 14463, \"end\": 14467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9999843149946646, \"rank\": 1.1269227806314814e-05, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The mental intensity just isn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t sustainable.\", \"from\": 14542, \"to\": 14588, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Add in the pressure to maintain an impossibly high standard and the physical disintegration of the body, and Ryan knows that the ride is far closer to the end than the beginning.\", \"from\": 14589, \"to\": 14767, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14698, \"end\": 14702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9999843149946646, \"rank\": 1.1269227806314814e-05, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s over, he might continue to coach throwers for the Razorbacks.\", \"from\": 14768, \"to\": 14842, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He might move to Nashville.\", \"from\": 14843, \"to\": 14870, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14860, \"end\": 14869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nashville_Predators\", \"score\": 0.9090762984487023, \"rank\": 0.09369596603535796, \"text\": \"Nashville\", \"types\": [\"Q4498974\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nashville_Predators\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nashville_Predators\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He might get married to his girlfriend, Meghan Clark, whose father is an Army general and who competed for Duke in pole vault.\", \"from\": 14871, \"to\": 14997, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14944, \"end\": 14948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Army\", \"score\": 0.9993541295055716, \"rank\": 0.000444907401660932, \"text\": \"Army\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Army\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Army\"}, {\"begin\": 14978, \"end\": 14982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zach_Duke\", \"score\": 0.8891644549364586, \"rank\": 0.07291408184699254, \"text\": \"Duke\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zach_Duke\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zach_Duke\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But one thing is certain.\", \"from\": 14999, \"to\": 15024, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After he leaves the throwing circle for the last time, Ryan Crouser is set: He will attempt to become a professional bass fisherman.\", \"from\": 15025, \"to\": 15157, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15080, \"end\": 15092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Crouser\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ryan Crouser\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Crouser\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Crouser\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A few weeks before leaving for Paris, Ryan sends Mitch a video.\", \"from\": 15159, \"to\": 15222, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15190, \"end\": 15195, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999760551603099, \"rank\": 2.3945412962676803e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 15197, \"end\": 15201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.8104413716881315, \"rank\": 0.23272290999051726, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}, {\"begin\": 15208, \"end\": 15213, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"score\": 0.9999998107715734, \"rank\": 1.646668813733447e-07, \"text\": \"Mitch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s his daily missive from his training session.\", \"from\": 15223, \"to\": 15274, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The video is of one attempt.\", \"from\": 15275, \"to\": 15303, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But Mitch sees progress, right then, that he hasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t seen in months.\", \"from\": 15304, \"to\": 15373, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15308, \"end\": 15313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"score\": 0.9999998107715734, \"rank\": 1.646668813733447e-07, \"text\": \"Mitch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then Ryan calls.\", \"from\": 15374, \"to\": 15390, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15379, \"end\": 15383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.8104413716881315, \"rank\": 0.23272290999051726, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cReally good throws today,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Ryan says.\", \"from\": 15391, \"to\": 15433, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15423, \"end\": 15427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.8104413716881315, \"rank\": 0.23272290999051726, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cSome of the best throws I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve had in a long time.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d The elbow?\", \"from\": 15434, \"to\": 15501, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cLittle better every day.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  After arriving in Paris, Ryan answered all the questions about becoming the first shot-putter to win three-straight Olympic golds.\", \"from\": 15502, \"to\": 15664, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15552, \"end\": 15557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999760551603099, \"rank\": 2.3945412962676803e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 15559, \"end\": 15563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.8104413716881315, \"rank\": 0.23272290999051726, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He iced his arm and elbow.\", \"from\": 15665, \"to\": 15691, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He reduced his usual daily training regimen of eight hours of work and 5,000 calories.\", \"from\": 15692, \"to\": 15778, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He did his physical therapy sessions, got massages.\", \"from\": 15779, \"to\": 15830, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Qualifying is Friday; the finals are Saturday.\", \"from\": 15832, \"to\": 15878, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ryan will be there, almost certainly, on the last day, deploying the glide technique he learned as a youngster in the barn in Oregon.\", \"from\": 15879, \"to\": 16012, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15879, \"end\": 15883, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.8104413716881315, \"rank\": 0.23272290999051726, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}, {\"begin\": 16005, \"end\": 16011, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oregon\", \"score\": 0.7951557613811485, \"rank\": 0.25410462357406377, \"text\": \"Oregon\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oregon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oregon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The greatest shot-putter who ever stepped inside a concrete circle just might lob that 16 pounds of sculpted steel as far as humanly possible.\", \"from\": 16013, \"to\": 16155, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And if he doesn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t, maybe it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s because he already has.\", \"from\": 16157, \"to\": 16214, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Loading recommendations...\", \"from\": 16216, \"to\": 16242, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please wait while we load personalized content recommendations  Greg Bishop is a senior writer for Sports Illustrated who has covered every kind of sport and every major event across six continents for more than two decades.\", \